Company Overview of Bain Capital Venture Fund 2007, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bain Capital Venture Fund 2007, L.P. specializes in venture capital investments in the healthcare and technology industry. It invests between $15 million and $18 million.


200 Clarendon StreetBoston, MA 02116United StatesFounded in 2006



Phone: 617-516-2000

Fax: 617-516-2010








